      <body>
         <p>
            <pb facs="1859_05_14_Kniffler_Dejima_von_Maclaine_Watson_Co_Batavia_1.tif" n="envelope"/>
            <seg rend="center">
               <stamp style="round" type="postal">
                  <placeName ref="K00508">Singapore</placeName> P. O.</stamp>
               <stamp style="round" type="postal">
                  <placeName ref="K00509">Hong Kong</placeName>
                  <gap quantity="3" unit="lines"/>
               </stamp>
               <lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">via <placeName ref="K00503">Sh<hi rend="underline">angh</hi>ai</placeName>
                  <lb/>
                  <stamp style="rectangular" type="postal">
                     <placeName ref="K00510">INDIA</placeName> PAID</stamp>
                  <lb/> Mess <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">L Kniffler &amp; Co</orgName>
                  <lb/>
                  <placeName ref="K00507">Decima</placeName>
                  <lb/>
                  <placeName ref="K00502">Jap<hi rend="underline">a</hi>n</placeName>
               </hi>
            </seg>
         </p>
         <p>
            <add style="writingMode: vertical-lr; textOrientation: sideways-right" resp="other" place="marginRight">
               <hi rend="latintype"> 1958<lb/>
                  <placeName ref="K00501">Batavia</placeName>, <date when="1858-05-14">14 Mai</date>
                  <lb/>
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01003">Maclaine Watson &amp; Co</orgName>
                  <lb/> R<hi rend="underline">
                     <date when="1859-06-18">18 Juni</date>
                  </hi>
                  <lb/>
                  <date when="1859-07">Juli</date>
               </hi>
            </add>
         </p>
         <pb facs="1859_05_14_Kniffler_Dejima_von_Maclaine_Watson_Co_Batavia_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <p>
            <term type="logistic" ref="K01538">Dublicate</term>
            <lb/>
            <seg rend="right">
               <placeName ref="K00501">Batavia</placeName>
               <date when="1859-05-14">14 May 1859</date>
            </seg>
            <lb/>
            <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">Mess. L Kniffler &amp; Co</orgName>
            <lb/>
            <seg rend="center">
               <placeName ref="K00507">Decima</placeName>
            </seg>
            <lb/> Gentlemen<lb/> Inclosed we have the pleasure to wait upon you<lb/> with
               <unclear>Bs</unclear> handing an Invoice of a small trial ship-<lb/> ment which we
            have addressed to your good care by<lb/> the "<name type="ship" ref="K01510">Nassau</name>" for sale on our amount on the recommen-<lb/> dation of your friends
            here.-.<lb/> The articles are all of first quality &amp; will we hope<lb/> be found well
            adapted for your market &amp;we sincerely<lb/> trust that the result may be such as to
            encourage<lb/> continued correspondance with yourgoodselves to our<lb/> mutual
            advantage<lb/> The method of making returns we must leave<lb/> to you We may remark
            however that importations<lb/> of <term type="goods" ref="K01511">Japan Wax</term> by
            the government have of late been<lb/> heavy and we have an unfavorable opinion of the
            future<lb/> Course of our market fort that article. <term type="goods" ref="K01511">Japan Wax</term> has<lb/> been sold lately à <measure type="currency" unit="gulden" quantity="40">
               <term type="measure" ref="K01512">f</term> 40</measure> on very long credit but it
            is<lb/> not expected that more than <measure type="currency" unit="gulden" quantity="30">
               <term type="measure" ref="K01512">f</term> 30</measure> á <measure type="currency" unit="gulden" quantity="34">
               <term type="measure" ref="K01512">f</term> 34</measure> will be realized<lb/> for the
            lot to be exposed for sale at the approaching<lb/> Government Auction &amp; it would not
            be safe to calculate<lb/> on higher prices. We are Gentlemen <seg rend="right"> Your obediently<lb/>
               <orgName type="firm" ref="K01003">Maclaine Watson &amp; Co.</orgName>
               <lb/>
            </seg>
         </p>
         <p>
            <seg rend="left"> We had intended to send<lb/> you some <term type="goods" ref="K01819">Black Pepper</term>
               <lb/> but none could be procured<lb/>
            </seg>
         </p>
         <pb facs="1859_05_14_Kniffler_Dejima_von_Maclaine_Watson_Co_Batavia_3.tif" n="3"/>
         <pb facs="1859_05_14_Kniffler_Dejima_von_Maclaine_Watson_Co_Batavia_4.tif" n="4"/>
